Quickstart
Prérequis / Prereqs

Rust stable, Node 18+, Yarn/PNPM, Anchor, Solana CLI

Devnet
solana config set --url https://api.devnet.solana.com
anchor build && anchor deploy
yarn --cwd sdk/ts install && yarn --cwd app install

Tests
anchor test
yarn --cwd sdk/ts test

🔀 Git & PR Process

Branches: feat/*, fix/*, chore/*

Commits: Conventional Commits (feat:, fix:, …)

PR = petits lots + checklist + tests

Reviews: 1 LGTM minimum

🗂️ Issues & Features

Labels: good-first-issue, hackathon, bounty, priority

Ouvrir une issue avec contexte, user story, critères d’acceptation (FR/EN)

🔒 Security / Sécurité

Veuillez signaler discrètement via SECURITY.md.
Please report privately via SECURITY.md.

